<div class="about-app">
  <h2>HOW DOES IT WORK?</h2>
  <h5 align="center"><u>Still got questions? don't worry!
  the website's functionalities are described in detail below:</u></h5>
 
  <h5>FREE USERS</h5>
  <p>Sing up with your <b>UTRGV</b> email to become a free user! as such, you will be able to see
