  <h5>PREMIUM USERS</h5>
  For a better experience, <b>upgrade</b> to become a PREMIUM user by paying a one-time fee of 5 USD. </br>
  PREMIUM users can create a personal profile and:

  <ul>
    <li>Input their name</li>
    <li>Add their skills and abilities (e.g. C++, HTML, Ruby)</li>
    <li>Specify their preferred location to work on (state)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>You can always come back and edit your profile if you need to make any changes.</br></br>
    As a PREMIUM user, internship opportunities will be "matched" to you: only those requiring
    your skills and abilities, as well as your preferred location, will be displayed. </br>
    From there, you can just click on <b>Apply</b> and will be automatically taken directly to the website.
  </p>
